Venom: The Last Dance stars Tom Hardy, Chiwetel Ejiofor, Juno Temple, Rhys Ifans, Peggy Lu, Alanna Ubach and Stephen Graham. snippet.title: 1st T20I | Highlights | Australia Tour Of England | 11th September 2024
snippet.description:
In the 1st T20I, England won the toss and elected to bowl first. Australia posted 179 runs and became all out by 19.3 overs. Travis Head was the top scorer with a terrific knock of 59 from 23 balls. Later, Australian bowlers troubled England batters and kept on taking wickets. England lost all 10 wickets for 151 runs as Australia sealed a 28-run win in the end.

Sitara, a lively orphan living with her brother, aunt, and uncle, finds joy in life's small things despite her aunt's poor treatment. Her aunt keeps her around because she has a share in the family's property.
Salar, the son of a wealthy businessman, is passionate about photography, which often earns him criticism from his family. With a pure heart, Salar is known for evading his responsibilities.
At her cousin's wedding, Sitara wrongly assumes Salar is the photographer. Salar develops a soft spot for Sitara after seeing how poorly she is treated. snippet.description:
A follow up to Aaj Bhi which ended up capturing millions of hearts upon its release back in 2020, Aaj Bhi 2 is just the perfect sequel to Aaj Bhi. Sung and composed by the sensational Vishal Mishra, Aaj Bhi 2 explores the raw, painful reality of loss. Vishal‚Äôs voice perfectly captures the loneliness, regret, and the overwhelming sadness of separation. Kaushal Kishore‚Äôs lyrics conveys the haunting reality of heartbreak and how healing is never a linear process, and one keeps getting sucked into their past searching for the moments where everything seemed right. Vishal‚Äôs composition and vocals brings Kaushal Kishore‚Äôs heartbreaking words alive and carries each lyric like a heavy weight, in what is an extremely powerful and emotional medley. Aaj Bhi 2 feels like a warm hug after a long rainy day.

Battle your way to the League and Global Tournaments to match against the best players in the world.

SEASONAL EVENTS
Unlock new Seasonal items like Tower Skins, Emotes and powerful Magic Items with the Season Pass and participate in fun Challenges that put your skills to the test!

See you in the Arena!

Sitara, a lively orphan living with her brother, aunt, and uncle, finds joy in life's small things despite her aunt's poor treatment. Her aunt keeps her around because she has a share in the family's property.
Salar, the son of a wealthy businessman, is passionate about photography, which often earns him criticism from his family. With a pure heart, Salar is known for evading his responsibilities.
